%20things'%20mantra%20and%20focus%20on%20'move%20at%20a%20responsible%20speed%20and%20fix%20things.'%20Tech%20should%20be%20used%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%2C%20and%20not%20just%20a%20way%20of%20beating%20others%20to%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECompanies%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20a%20vacuum%20and%20their%20actions%20have%20consequences%20for%20individuals%20and%20society%2C%20Wachter%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20not%20a%20sandbox%20or%20a%20big%20field%20experiment%2C%20and%20so%20we%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20what%20products%20are%20opened%20up%20for%20the%20market%20and%20when%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Google%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-firestorm-big-tech-ai-arms-race-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709717401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7121d6080194819fc76df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-firestorm-big-tech-ai-arms-race-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sergey%20Brin%20said%20the%20images%20were%20likely%20down%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20testing.%20It's%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20fierce%20AI%20war%20that's%20embroiling%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-firestorm-big-tech-ai-arms-race-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20desserts%20take%20center%20stage%20at%20Ambani%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709717144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108264560%2Cimgsize-30238.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22