20Minister%20opened%20several%20new%20routes%20of%20Kolkata%20Metro%20and%20also%20took%20a%20ride%20in%20it%20while%20interacting%20with%20several%20schoolgoers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20modernising%20public%20transport%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20his%20government.%20Several%20generations%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20grown%20up%20looking%20at%20Kolkata%20Metro.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20came%20to%20Kolkata%20as%20a%20child%2C%20seeing%20the%20Metro%20was%20an%20attraction.%20But%20today%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Metro%20is%20also%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20fast%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20works.%20In%20the%2040%20years%20before%202014%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Metro%20route%20expanded%20to%2028%20km.%20But%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%2031%20km%20of%20Metro%20route%20have%20been%20added.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20worked%20very%20honestly%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Bengal%20and%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20a%20part%2C%20are%20scared%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20to%20return%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20losing%20their%20sleep%20and%20their%20balance%2C%20so%20they%20have%20started%20abusing%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20now%20saying%20that%20I%20talk%20against%20dynastic%20politics%20because%20I%20have%20no%20family.%20They%20want%20to%20know%20where%20my%20family%20is.%20These%20dynasts%20should%20come%20here.%20This%20is%20Modi%20ka%20parivar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20BJP's%20campaign%20to%20counter%20RJD%20patriarch%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20%26quot%3BModi%20has%20no%20family%26quot%3B%20jab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20at%20the%20women%20in%20the%20crowd%2C%20he%20said%20the%20mothers%2C%20sisters