t%20takes%20a%20decision.%20Shahjahan%20was%20earlier%20arrested%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%2052%20days.%20While%20the%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20him%2C%20the%20BJP%20says%20people%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20who%20have%20accused%20him%20and%20his%20aides%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%2C%20will%20get%20no%20justice%20till%20central%20agency%20grills%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20trusts%20leaders%20who%20commit%20atrocities%2C%20but%20not%20the%20women%20of%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BWomen%20from%20Bengal%20and%20the%20country%20are%20outraged.%20This%20storm%20won't%20remain%20restricted%20to%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20will%20reach%20the%20whole%20Bengal.%20Bengal's%20Nari%20Shakti%20has%20set%20out%20to%20destroy%20Trinamool's%20Mafia%20rule.%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20shown%20that%20only%20BJP%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20women%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20government%2C%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20appeasement%20and%20extortionists%2C%20will%20never%20help%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20several%20welfare%20schemes%20launched%20for%20women%20have%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20met%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20island.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20public%20meeting%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20met%20a%20few%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali.%20They%20narrated%20their%20ordeal%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20heard%20them%20patiently%20like%20a%20father%20figure.%20The%20victims%20were%20very%20emotional%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20party%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709715840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqpcjntno_modi-barasat-split_625x300_06_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fi