%20trench%20ahead%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20to%20BI%20at%20a%20training%20site%20for%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20the%20south%20of%20England.%20At%20the%20request%20of%20the%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Davidson%20is%20referred%20to%20only%20by%20his%20surname.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavidson%20said%20training%20on%20trenches%20and%20drone%20warfare%20are%20among%20the%20areas%20that%20have%20changed%20the%20most%2C%20based%20on%20developments%20coming%20out%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20volume%20of%20trenches%20in%20Ukraine%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-battlefield-like-world-war-i-but-with-terrifying-drones-2023-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20battlefields%20there%20have%20often%20been%20compared%20to%20those%20of%20World%20War%20I%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20dug%20trenches%2C%20with%20soldiers%20hiding%20in%2C%20launching%20attacks%20from%2C%20and%20fighting%20each%20other%20in%20the%20miles%20of%20deep%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-winter-long-nights-russia-vulnerable-drone-pilots-lack-gear-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDrones%2520are%2520leading%2520to%2520more%2Conly%2520appears%2520to%2520be%2520growing.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatured%20more%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20than%20in%20any%20other%20conflict%20in%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20soldiers%20saying%20that%20there%20are%20often%20hundreds%20in%20the%20sky%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-pilot-says-so-many-drones-troops-cant-advance-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520Ukrainian%2520drone%2520operator%2520said%2520there%2520are%2520so%2520many%2520drones%2Cknow%2520how%2520to%2520move%2520forward.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elittle%20opportunity%20to%20move%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20US%20soldier%20fighting%20with%20Ukraine%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-bakhmut-resembled-world-war-one-because-drones-us-veteran-2023-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20drones%20was%20the%20reason%20why%20so%20many%20trenches%20had%20been%20dug%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20soldiers%20were%20desperate%20to%20find%20somewhere%20to%20hide%20out%20of%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavidson%20said%20Ukrainians%20%26quot%3Bnow%20break%20into%20smaller%20teams%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20down%20trenches%20instead%20of%20a%20larger%20line%20of%20people%20all%20advancing%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20partly%20because%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20just%20so%20unsure%20with%20booby%20traps%20and%20things%20like%20that%2C%20that%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20trench%20line%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20dispersion%20is%20like%20a%20method%20of%20protection%20from%20booby%20traps.%20So%20it%20just%20means%20that%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20all%20collectively%20get%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20and%20partner%20countries%20have%20trained%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20Ukrainian%20troops%20in%20the%20UK%20since%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavidson%20said%20the%20training%20process%20is%20a%20collaborative%20one%2C%20where%20methods%20used%20by%20Ukrainians%20against%20Russia%20are%20integrated%20and%20can%20even%20be%20incorporated%20into%20UK%20military%20doctrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20allows%20them%20to%20give%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20%26quot%3Bmore%20accurate%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20in%20some%20areas%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20we%20actually%20found%20is%20that%20we%20were%20learning%20more%20off%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20trench%20warfare%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20both%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20international%20partner%20forces%20started%20doing%20this%20training%2C%20we%20had%20doctrine%20that%20was%20dated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20are%20now%20quickly%20learning%20from%20what%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20areas%20like%20trench%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%2C%20we%20%26quot%3Bquickly%20identified%20that%20the%20battle%20space%20over%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20what%20they%20were%20seeing%20with%20the%20Russians%20was%20very%20different%20to%20what%20we%20were%20teaching%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Davidson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-attack-trenches-drone-first-protection-russia-boobytrap-trainer-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709715486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7811ea610a9069d5b44ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-attack-trenches-drone-first-protection-russia-boobytrap-trainer-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20are%20using%20drones%20to%20lead%20them%20into%20trenches%2C%20a%20military%20trainer%20said%2C%20another%20sign%20of%20their%20ubiquitousness%20on%20the%20battlefield.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-soldiers-attack-trenches-drone-first-protection-russia-boobytrap-trainer-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Rising%20Irish%20Stars%20Behind%20the%20Camera%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709715360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIrish-Talent-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fpost_type