norm%20in%20China%20is%20to%20only%20vacation%20during%20pre-defined%20weeks%20blocked%20off%20by%20your%20employer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20topic%2C%20raised%20by%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20politician%2C%20went%20viral%20after%20state%20media%20appeared%20to%20voice%20support.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Hong%20Kong%20politician's%20recent%20commentary%20on%20paid%20time%20off%20has%20sparked%20a%20debate%20in%20China%20on%20annual%20leave%20%E2%80%94%20or%20rather%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenneth%20Fok%2C%20a%20Hong%20Kong-based%20member%20of%20China's%20National%20People's%20Congress%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Frain%2Fa%2F20240304A096PE00%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20state%20media%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Monday%20that%20the%20country%20should%20gradually%20increase%20paid%20time%20off%20for%20young%20workers%2C%20giving%20them%20one%20extra%20day%20of%20entitled%20leave%20for%20every%20year%20of%20work%20experience%20they%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mohrss.gov.cn%2Fxxgk2020%2Ffdzdgknr%2Fzcfg%2Ffg%2F202011%2Ft20201103_394938.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurrent%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20give%20employees%20five%20days%20of%20annual%20paid%20time%20off%2C%20which%20increases%20to%2010%20days%20after%20they%20have%20worked%2010%20years%2C%20and%2015%20days%20if%20they%20have%20worked%20for%2020%20years%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFok's%20proposal%20would%20let%20young%20workers%20scale%20their%20annual%20leave%20from%20five%20to%2010%20days%20until%20they%20hit%20the%2010-year%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20five-day%20statutory%20annual%20leave%20cannot%20ensure%20they%20have%20adequate%20rest.%20If%20things%20go%20on%20like%20this%2C%20it%20will%20impact%20the%20public's%20spiritual%20quality%2C%20overall%20style%2C%20society's%20level%20of%20grit%2C%26quot%3B%20Fok%20said%2C%20per%20China%20Youth%20Daily%2C%20a%20party-run%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFok%20said%20he