0interests%20have%20been%20damaged%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20went%20viral%2C%20charting%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Weibo's%20hot%20search%20list%20with%20110%20million%20views%2C%20per%20data%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20widespread%20response%20to%20this%20shows%20how%20we've%20suffered%20under%20the%20996%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1647486362%2FO3IraaTNU%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20one%20blogger.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20office%20workers%20have%20not%20enjoyed%20a%20weekend%20off%3F%20How%20many%20laborers%20have%20yet%20to%20receive%20all%20their%20overtime%20pay%3F%20How%20many%20people%20have%20already%20forgotten%20what%20annual%20leave%20is%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'I%20can't%20even%20get%20a%20two-day%20break%20every%20week'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-work-culture-schedule-popular-in-china-explained-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E996%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20popularized%20by%20figures%20like%20Alibaba%20founder%20Jack%20Ma%2C%20obligates%20employees%20to%20work%20from%209%20a.m.%20to%209%20p.m.%20for%20six%20days%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20an%20overtime%20work%20culture%20that%20was%20for%20a%20time%20celebrated%20as%20a%20driver%20of%20Chinese%20growth%20but%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisenchanted-chinese-youth-join-a-mass-movement-to-lie-flat-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epushback%20from%20disgruntled%20youth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20debate%20soon%20hinged%20on%20whether%20bosses%20even%20allowed%20young%20employees%20to%20take%20mandatory%20leave%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20even%20enforce%20the%20labor%20law%2C%20so%20increasing%20annual%20leave%20directly%20is%20simply%20wishful%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D