s.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Faunty-collapsed-i-dialled-cheteswar-pujara-r-ashwins-wife-prithi-narrates-rajkot-test-emergency-5185868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20wife%20Prithi%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20Indian%20cricketer's%20mother%20collapsed%20during%20the%20Rajkot%20Test%2C%20prompting%20the%20off-spinner%20to%20leave%20the%20match%20against%20England%20midway.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Opens%20Kolkata's%20Underwater%20Metro%2C%20India's%20First%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20Bengal%20Police%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20over%20the%20custody%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20address%20a%20meeting%20today%20at%20Barasat.%20Barasat%20is%20in%20the%20same%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20as%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20an%20island%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20talking%20point%20in%20Bengal%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20event%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20attended%20by%20some%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20which%20has%20made%20national%20headlines%20over%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%20against%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20led%20by%20Shahjahan.%20The%20BJP%20plans%20to%20get%20women%20from%20the%20island%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20event%20as%20it%20slams%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20over%20women's%20safety%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20Bengal%20comes%20amid%20a%20face-off%20between%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20state%20police%20over%20the%20custody%20of%20Shahjahan.%20Arrested%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%2052%20days%2C%20he%20has%20been%20expelled%20by%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20party.%20He%20is%20currently%20with%20Bengal%20police%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20people%20of%20the%20island%20will%20not%20get%20any%20justice%20till%20he%20is%20grilled%20by%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20yesterday%20directed%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan's%20custody%20to%20CBI%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20has%20become%20imperative%20and%20absolutely%20necessary%20for%20doing%20complete%20justice%20and%20enforcing%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20public%20in%20general%20and%20the%20public%20of%20the%20locality%20that%20the%20cases%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20for%20investigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%20order%20and%20sought%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%20The%20request%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20was%20turned%20down%2C%20and%20the%20Bengal%20government%20was%20asked%20to%20mention%20its%20plea%20before%20the%20Registrar-General%20for%20a%20date%2C%20as%20per%20rules.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20they%20were%20given%20sufficient%20time%20to%20seek%20legal%20remedy%20against%20the%20high%20court%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20police%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20refused%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20strongman%20to%20a%20CBI%20team%20that%20had%20reached%20its%20office%20to%20take%20custody.%20The%20state%20police%20maintained%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20handover%20must%20take%20place%20only%20after%20a%20court%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20keep%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20issue%20alive%20as%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20polls.%20For%20the%20party%20to%20achieve%20its%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20it%20must%20maximise%20its%20wins%20in%20Opposition-ruled%20states%20such%20as%20Bengal.%20And%20the%20serious%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20leaders%20have%20come%20as%20a%20great%20political%20opportunity%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Barasat%20event%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20inaugurated%20several%20routes%20of%20Kolkata%20Metro.%20The%20highlight%20is%20the%20country's%20first%20underwater%20Metro%20rail%20stretch%20-%20the%20train%20will%20pass%20under%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Ganga%20river.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20took%20a%20ride%20in%20the%20Metro%2C%20and%20visuals%20showed%20him%20chatting%20with%20a%20group%20of%20schoolgoers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709709300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm0rc4kb_pm-in-metro_625x300_06_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-sheikh-shahjahan-pm-narendra-modi-amid-tug-of-war-over-sandeshkhali-strongman-pm-on-mamata-banerjees-turf-5185338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20Bengal%20Police%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20over%20the%20custody%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20address%20a%20meeting%20today%20at%20Barasat%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-sheikh-shahjahan-pm-narendra-modi-amid-tug-of-war-over-sandeshkhali-strongman-pm-on-mamata-banerjees-turf-5185338%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-sheikh-shahjahan-pm-narendra-modi-amid-tug-of-war-over-sandeshkhali-strongman-pm-on-mamata-banerjees-turf-5185338%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-sheikh-shahjahan-pm-narendra-modi-amid-tug-of-war-over-sandeshkhali-strongman-pm-on-mamata-banerjees-turf-5