0charging%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20hour%20at%20Bengaluru's%20UB%20City%20Mall%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20on%20social%20media.%20Users%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22HADI%20KHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cert-In%20warns%20of%20critical%20security%20flaw%20in%20these%20two%20govt%20apps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108259561%2Cimgsize-766211.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fcert-in-warns-of-critical-security-flaw-in-these-two-government-apps%2Farticleshow%2F108259561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20CERT-In%20has%20reported%20'high'%20severity%20security%20flaws%20in%20government%20apps%20USB%20Pratirodh%20and%20AppSamvid.%20These%20vulnerabilities%20can%20allow%20hackers%20to%20take%20control%20and%20execute%20arbitrary%20code.%20Download%20the%20latest%20versions%20to%20stay%20protected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fcert-in-warns-of-critical-security-flaw-in-these-two-government-apps%2Farticleshow%2F108259561.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court's%20%26quot%3BWaste%20Bin%26quot%3B%20Rap%20Over%20Deforestation%20In%20Corbett%20Tiger%20Reserve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20and%20illegal%20construction%20in%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20public%20trust%20had%20been%20thrown%20into%20the%20waste%20bin.%C2%A0Pulling%20up%20former%20state%20minister%20Harak%20Singh%20Rawat%20and%20former%20divisional%20forest%20officer%20Kishan%20Chand%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20that%20will%20recommend%20steps%20to%20mitigate%20the%20damage%20and%20recover%20the%20cost%20from%20those%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20Justice%20PK%20Mishra%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20environment%20activist%20and%20lawyer%20Gaurav%20Bansal.%20Mr%20Bansal%20had%20challenged%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government's%20proposal%20for%20a%20tiger%20safari%20and%20a%20zoo%20with%20caged%20animals%20inside%20the%20national%20park.%20The%20matter%20brought%20under%20the%20spotlight%20illegal%20construction%20and%20deforestation%20inside%20the%20national%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20started%20with%20a%20quote%20from%20the%20epic%20Mahabharata%2C%20which%20means%20that%20a%20forest%20protects%20the%20tiger%20and%20the%20tiger%20protects%20the%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tiger%20safari%20in%20the%20core%20area%2C%20it%20said%2C%20will%20be%20contrary%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20tiger%20conservation.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20safari%20tours%20in%20the%20buffer%20zone%20of%20the%20popular%20national%20park%2C%20citing%20the%20employment%20it%20may%20generate.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20such%20safari%20tours%20should%20follow%20the%20necessary%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20Mr%20Rawat%20and%20Mr%20Chand%2C%20the%20court%20said%20this%20is%20a%20case%20where%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians%20threw%20public%20trust%20doctrine%20in%20the%20waste%20bin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%2C%20in%20blatant%20disregard%20of%20the%20law%20and%20for%20commercial%20purposes%2C%20indulged%20in%20mass%20felling%20of%20trees%20to%20construct%20buildings%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20promotion%20of%20tourism%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bamazed%20at%20the%20audacity%26quot%3B%20in%20giving%20rules%20a%20go-by.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%206%2C000%20trees%20were%20felled%20in%20the%20national%20park%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20while%20figures%20show%20substantial%20reduction%20in%20poaching%20of%20tigers%2C%20%26quot%3Bground%20realities%20cannot%20be%20denied%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20appointed%20a%20three-member%20committee%20to%20provide%20suggestions%20for%20efficient%20management%20of%20tiger%20reserves%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20asked%20the%20panel%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20already%20probing%20the%20matter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20probe%20will%20only%20lead%20to%20finding%20out%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%20We%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20State%20cannot%20run%20away%20from%20the%20responsibility%20of%20restoring%20the%20status%20of%20the%20forest%20from%20when%20damage%20was%20done%20and%20recover%20it%20from%20the%20ones%20who%20committed%20the%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20asking%20the%20central%20agency%20to%20file%20a%20status%20report%20in%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flf6403lo_jim-corbett-national-park_625x300_06_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-waste-bin-rap-over-deforestation-in-corbett-tiger-reserve-5185757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20and%20illegal%20construction%20in%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20public%20trust%20had%20been%20thrown%20into%20the%20waste%20bin%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n