udy%20suggests%20this%20could%20be%201%2C850%20times%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20lies%20in%20tyre%20wear%2C%20with%20Emission%20Analytics%20pointing%20out%20that%20EVs'%20heavier%20weight%20causes%20tyres%20to%20deteriorate%20faster%2C%20releasing%20harmful%20chemicals%20into%20the%20air.%20This%20is%20because%20most%20tires%20are%20made%20from%20synthetic%20rubber%20derived%20from%20crude%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20highlights%20the%20impact%20of%20battery%20weight.%20EVs%20typically%20have%20heavier%20batteries%20compared%20to%20traditional%20petrol%20engines.%20This%20extra%20weight%20puts%20more%20strain%20on%20the%20brakes%20and%20tyres%2C%20accelerating%20wear%20and%20tear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cites%20the%20Tesla%20Model%20Y%20and%20Ford%20F-150%20Lightning%20as%20examples%2C%20both%20featuring%20batteries%20weighing%20around%201%2C800%20pounds.%20The%20study%20claims%20that%20tyre%20wear%20emissions%20from%20an%20EV%20with%20a%20half-tonne%20(1%2C100%20pounds)%20battery%20could%20be%20over%20400%20times%20higher%20than%20exhaust%20emissions%20from%20a%20modern%20petrol%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20focus%20has%20traditionally%20been%20on%20tailpipe%20emissions%2C%20this%20study%20suggests%20that%20particle%20pollution%20from%20brakes%20and%20tyres%20needs%20to%20be%20considered%20when%20evaluating%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709708040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fq3722mug_electric-vehicles-bloomberg_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felectric-vehicles-emit-more-particle-pollution-than-petrol-diesel-cars-claims-study-5185055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electric%20vehicles%20release%20more%20toxic%20particles%20into%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20are%20worse%20for%20the%20environment%20than%20their%20fossil%20fuel-powered%20counterparts%2C%20according%20to%20a%20resurfaced%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felectric-vehicles-emit-more-particle-pollution-than-petrol-diesel-cars-claims-study-5185055%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felectric-vehicles-emit-more-particle-pollution-than-petrol-diesel-cars-claims-study-5185055%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Felectric-vehicles-emit-more-particle-pollution-than-petrol-diesel-cars-claims-study-5185055%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20used%20cable%20ties%20to%20detain%20children%20-%20police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709707754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF284%2Fproduction%2F_132848026_240306cabletiedkidsstill2v2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68487304%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State%20officials%20say%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bappalled%26quot%3B%20by%20footage%20appearing%20to%20show%20two%20children%20tied%20up%20and%20crying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68487304%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68487304.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68487304.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20fought%20legal%20battle%20against%20Sara%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709707706000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108259153%2Cimgsize-32342.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhishek-kapoor-says-he-had-to-fight-a-legal-battle-against-sara-ali-khan-as-she-gave-sushant-singh-rajput-starrer-kedar