%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI-M)%20are%20some%20examples%20of%20cadre-based%20parties%20in%20India.%20A%20few%20may%20have%20weakened%2C%20but%20arguably%2C%20if%20the%20BSP%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20are%20still%20alive%20today%2C%20it%20is%20in%20large%20measure%20due%20to%20their%20cadre-based%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20Can't%20Guide%20the%20Future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20in%20the%20Congress%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20making%20history%20the%20guide%20to%20the%20future.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG6BqPOj8Jl0%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20use%20social%20media%20in%20the%201920s%20because%20social%20media%20did%20not%20exist.%20Given%20what%20a%20prolific%20writer%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20was%2C%20had%20he%20been%20alive%20today%2C%20we%20can%20be%20certain%20he%20would%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20using%20social%20media%20to%20persuade%20the%20public%20in%20his%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20rethink%20its%20party%20organisation.%20This%20is%20not%20something%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20addressed%20with%20a%20simple%20membership%20drive%2C%20because%20it%20is%20pointless%20to%20add%20new%20members%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20new%20imagination%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20party%20organisation%20is%20shaped%20and%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20State%20Where%20Congress%20Model%20Is%20Different%3A%20Kerala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20resembles%20that%20of%20cadre-based%20parties.%20And%20no%2C%20it%20is%20not%20Karnataka.%20It's%20Kerala.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20there%20evolved%20in%20response%20to%20the%20cadres%20of%20the%20CPI(M).%20They%20had%20to.%20It's%20how%20they%20survived%20-%20though%20today%20even%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20weakened%2C%20as%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20the%20Congress%20evolved%20a%20new%20organisational%20structure%20in%20Kerala%20in%20response%20to%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20do%20so%20nationally%20too%20in%20response%20to%20the%20post-2014%20version%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20The%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20today%20has%20such%20a%20formidable%20party%20organisation%20that%20we%20rarely%20hear%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsewak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20workers%20in%20the%20party's%20election%20campaigns%20anymore.%20It%20is%20well-known%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20expanded%20its%20party%20organisation%20manifold%20since%202014.%20What%20is%20less%20appreciated%20is%20what%20this%20organisation%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20and%20analysts%20focus%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20speeches%20and%20campaigns%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20media%2C%20as%20the%20factors%20behind%20the%20BJP's%20victories.%20But%20the%20huge%20army%20of%20party%20workers%20going%20from%20door%20to%20door%20does%20not%20get%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20man%20cannot%20reach%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20For%20the%20common%20man%2C%20the%20party%20is%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20lives%20next%20door.%20The%20party%20worker%20does%20what%20she%20can%20for%20the%20people%20living%20in%20her%20polling%20booth%2C%20all%20year%20round.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it's%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20can%20pull%20in%20the%20BJP%20vote%20as%20a%20personal%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Tech-Savvy%20Army%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20always%20been%20true%20of%20political%20parties.%20Apart%20from%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20party%20workers%20to%20a%20massive%2020%20per%20booth%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20centralised%20and%20turbo-charged%20this%20army%20with%20technology.%20Party%20workers%20are%20given%20regular%20campaign%20tasks%2C%20at%20least%20once%20a%20month%2C%20to%20reach%20every%20home.%20Whether%20it's%20G20%20or%20Ram%20Mandir%20or%20free%20food%20grains%2C%20the%20party%20worker%20will%20take%20the%20message%20to%20every%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20still%20loses%20some%20state%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20because%20in%20a%20given%20situation%2C%20the%20party%20may%20suffer%20narrative%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20indefensible%20anti-incumbency%20or%20leadership%20challenges%2C%20say%2C%20a%20lightweight%20chief%20minister.%20But%20even%20in%20such%20scenarios%2C%20the%20BJP%20invariably%20retains%20a%20strong%20vote%20share%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20workers%20who%20bring%20in%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20are%20answerable%20for%20their%20tasks%20to%20the%20party%20leadership%20centrally%2C%20and%20not%20to%20local%20leaders.%20The%20BJP%20manages%20this%20centralisation%20through%20technology.%20These%20days%2C%20the%20party%20uses%20an%20app%20called%20'Saral'%2C%20where%20workers%20have%20to%20upload%20selfies%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20actually%20organised%20a%20small%20gathering%20to%20make%20people%20hear%20the%20fortnightly%20episode%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20%3Cem%3EMann%20Ki%20Baat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshow.%20If%20a%20worker%20doesn't%20perform%20well%2C%20she%20can%20be%20replaced%20-%20after%20all%2C%20there%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20cadres%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Risk%20Of%20Shifting%20Loyalties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20lone%20Congress%20worker%20in%20a%20polling%20booth%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20local%20Congress%20leader.%20If%20the%20Congress%20leader%20switches%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20so%20does%20the%20worker%20and%20the%20votes%20she%20possibly%20commands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20or%20cannot%20create%20a%20new%20centralised%20party%20organisation%20like%20the%20BJP's.%20In%20fact%2C%20I'll%20go%20a%20step%20further%20and%20say%20that%20the%20Congress%20party's%20long-term%20revival%20is%20impossible%20unless%20it%20creates%20a%20new%20tech-driven%20centralised%20party%20organisation%20where%20workers%20are%20held%20accountable%20for%20door-to-door%20campaigning%20through%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20%3Cem%3Eif%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20%3Cem%3Ewhen%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Now%20is%20a%20good%20time%20to%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Naresh%20Arora%20is%20an%20accomplished%20political%20strategist.%20He%20has%20worked%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20for%20Haryana%2C%20Assam%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20elections)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709706000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fbjp-flags-650_650x400_71520085058.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20common%20man%20cannot%20reach%20Narendra%20Modi%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20For%20the%20common%20man%2C%20the%20party%20is%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20lives%20next%20door.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20understand%20this%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-cadre-based-model-5185775%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-revival-is-impossible-without-a-