20Connor%20moved%20to%20Australia%2015%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3EBaishakhi%20Connor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBaishakhi%20Connor%20spent%20over%20a%20year%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConnor%20looks%20back%20on%20the%20resume%20and%20what%20she%20would%20change%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20important%20to%20tailor%20resumes%20according%20to%20local%20norms%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftopmate.io%2Fbaishakhiconnor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaishakhi%20Connor%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20working%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20seven%20years%20%E2%80%94%20first%20in%20tech%20and%20then%20investment%20banking%20%E2%80%94%20when%20she%20was%20laid%20off%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20married%20an%20Australian%20and%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Australia.%20Connor%20had%20prior%20work%20experience%20in%20India%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20try%20to%20find%20work%20in%20her%20new%20home%20country%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20stage%2C%20despite%20having%20quite%20a%20significant%20global%20career%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20break%20into%20the%20Australian%20job%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20her%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20meeting%20with%20a%20professional%20resume%20consultant%20to%20land%20a%20job%20in%20Melbourne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReflecting%20back%20and%20now%20leading%20and%20building%20teams%20myself%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20I%20perhaps%20didn't%20put%20myself%20forward%20in%20the%20best%20way%20for%20this%20job%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20her%20job-application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20resume%20followed%20a%20format%20popular%20with%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20students%3A%20It%20was%20one%20page%20long%20and%20written%20in%20font%20size%208.%20It%20starts%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bacademic%20qualifications%26quot%3B%20section%20before%20moving%20on%20to%20experiences%20and%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20resume%20she%20used%20to%20apply%20to%20jobs%20in%202009.%20She%20has%20since%20changed%20her%20last%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221275%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Resume%20sample%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7e869ce7f1785b2e6b11e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202009%20resume%20Connor%20used%20to%20apply%20to%20jobs%20in%20Australia%3Cp%3EBaishakhi%20Connor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResume%20mistakes%20Connor%20made%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%2015%20years%20later%2C%20Connor%20reexamined%20her%20resume%20and%20said%20she%20would%20do%20several%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20literally%20cringed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20got%20that%20resume%20today%20I%20would%20not%20have%20called%20that%20person%20for%20an%20interview.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20she%20would%20change%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20a%20summary%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20missing%20summary%20or%20a%20profile%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said%20of%20her%20resume.%20Recruiters%20today%20often%20open%20multiple%20positions%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20and%20having%20a%20summary%2C%20which%20is%20a%20two-to-three-line%20pitch%20on%20who%20you%20are%2C%20allows%20them%20to%20help%20place%20a%20candidate%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperience%20first%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20been%20in%20investment%20banking%20and%20tech%20consulting%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said.%20Despite%20having%20seven%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20she%20started%20her%20resume%20with%20academic%20qualifications%2C%20and%20had%20sections%20on%20research%20papers%20and%20leadership%20positions%20she%20held%20in%20college.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20seems%20like%20a%20very%20new%20university%20student%20kind%20of%20resume%20in%20hindsight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETranslate%20your%20achievements%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BIIM%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20into%2C%20it's%20very%20selective.%20But%20when%20I%20came%20here%20people%20did%20not%20know%20what%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said%20about%20the%20Indian%20university%20where%20she%20pursued%20her%20masters.%20If%20you're%20applying%20to%20a%20job%20overseas%2C%20help%20a%20foreign%20employer%20understand%20the%20scale%20or%20prestige%20of%20your%20background.%20For%20example%3A%20%26quot%3BTranslate%20to%20say%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%2410%20billion%20turnover%20company%20or%20it%20has%2050%2C000%20employees%20to%20give%20people%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20size%20or%20complexity%20of%20the%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECater%20to%20local%20employers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BEach%20country%20has%20its%20own%20lingo%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said.%20In%20retrospect%2C%20she%20would%20write%20%26quot%3BCareer%20Highlights%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BWork%20Experience%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20in%20Australia%2C%20%26quot%3Bwork%20experience%26quot%3B%20is%20something%20school%20students%20do%20for%20free%20to%20understand%20the%20industry%2C%20Connor%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20employees%20in%20Australia%20prefer%20multi-page%20resumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Connor%20revamped%20her%20resume%20with%20a%20summary%20and%20highlights%20of%20her%20professional%20experience%2C%20she%20said%20she%20began%20landing%20more%20interviews%20and%20got%20her%20first%20offer%20three%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnor%20went%20on%20to%20work%20with%20large%20businesses%20within%20consulting%20and%20consumer%20goods%20before%20taking%20on%20her%20current%20role%20as%20an%20executive%20at%20a%20retail%20chain.%20Connor%20also%20runs%20a%20career-building%20consultancy%20that%20reviews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftopmate.io%2Fbaishakhiconnor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresumes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20top%20tip%20for%20resumes%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20next%20story%20you're%20trying%20to%20write%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20use%20resumes%20to%20just%20collate%20what%20they've%20done%20in%20the%20past%2C%20whereas%20the%20bigger%20job%20for%20a%20resume%20is%20to%20market%20you%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-mistakes-looking-for-jobs-overseas-india-australia-interview-recruitment-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709705920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7ec22ce7f1785b2e6b168%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-mistakes-looking-for-jobs-overseas-india-australia-interview-recruitment-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20literally%20cringed%2C%26quot%3B%20Baishakhi%20Connor%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20got%20that%20resume%20today%20I%20would%20not%20have%20called%20that%20person%20for%20an%20interview.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A213%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-mistakes-looking-for-jobs-overseas-india-australia-interview-recruitment-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20inaugurates%20India's%201st%20underwater%20metro%20in%20Kolkata%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170970514000