g%20government%20may%20be%20formed%20with%20representatives%20from%20various%20political%20parties.%20Even%20if%20the%20unity%20government%20formula%20fails%2C%20the%20commission%20may%20suggest%20holding%20fresh%20elections%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20term%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%2021st%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20suggestions%2C%20which%20had%20favoured%20simultaneous%20polls%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20would%20save%20public%20money.%20However%2C%20it%20had%20said%20the%20same%20is%20not%20possible%20with%20the%20existing%20constitutional%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20said%C2%A0the%20proposal%20can%20only%20be%20materialised%20by%20the%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20as%20it%20would%2C%20over%20time%2C%20work%20out%20a%20formula%20to%20synchronise%20all%20assembly%20elections%2C%20either%20by%20extending%20or%20reducing%20the%20tenures%20of%20respective%20state%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709702561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flaw-commissions-final-report-on-simultaneous-polls-likely-by-mid-march-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20all%20likelihood%2C%20the%20Commission%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20its%20report%20ready%20before%20the%20schedule%20for%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flaw-commissions-final-report-on-simultaneous-polls-likely-by-mid-march-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Peru%20PM%20resigns%20after%20recording%20with%20woman%20leaked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709701901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https