20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Ftaylor-swift-singapore-eras-tour-concerts-asia-b2507171.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20exclusivity%20clause%20negotiated%20by%20Singapore%20Prime%20Minister%20Lee%20Hsien%20Loong%2C%20which%20forbids%20Ms%20Swift%20from%20performing%20anywhere%20else%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20has%20led%20to%20a%20backlash%20among%20the%20city-state's%20neighbours%20over%20the%20arrangement%2C%20which%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20about%2014%20million%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Lover'%20singer%20is%20performing%20six%20shows%20in%20Singapore%20from%20March%202%20to%209.%20Thailand%20and%20the%20Philippines%20have%20criticised%20the%20same%20and%20have%20branded%20the%20deal%20%26quot%3Bunfriendly%26quot%3B.%20They%20have%20expressed%20that%20they%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20the%20increase%20in%20tourism%20linked%20to%20her%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThailand%20Prime%20Minister%20Srettha%20Thavisin%20said%20that%20he%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20agreement%20that%20Ms%20Swift%20will%20not%20do%20any%20other%20shows%20in%20the%20Association%20of%20South%20East%20Asian%20Nations%20(ASEAN).%20Citing%20a%20concert%20promoter%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Singapore%20offered%20Ms%20Swift%20up%20to%20US%243%20million%20per%20concert%20if%20she%20did%20not%20play%20anywhere%20else%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsingapore-has-done-deal-so-taylor-swift-cant-perform-in-any-other-countries-in-southeast-asia-13072902%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSingapore%2520has%2520done%2520a%2520deal%2Cof%2520South%2520East%2520Asian%2520Nations.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Singapore%20government%20is%20astute.%20If%20she%20came%20to%20Thailand%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20cheaper%20to%20organise%20it%20here%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20she%20would%20be%20able%20to%20attract%20more%20sponsors%20and%20tourists%20to%20Thailand.%20Even%20though%20we%20would%20have%20to%20subsidise%20at%20least%20500m%20baht%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Thai%20PM%20said%20in%20a%20keynote%20speech%20at%20the%20iBusiness%20Forum%202024%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20known%20this%2C%20I%20would%20have%20brought%20the%20shows%20to%20Thailand.%20Concerts%20can%20generate%20added%20value%20for%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilipino%20lawmaker%20Joey%20Salceda%20said%20that%20the%20deal%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bisn't%20what%20good%20neighbours%20do%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOur%20countries%20are%20good%20friends.%20That's%20why%20actions%20like%20that%20hurt.%26quot%3B%20Although%20he%20mentioned%20that%20it%20boosted%20Singapore's%20economy%2C%20it%20was%20done%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20expense%20of%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20which%20could%20not%20attract%20their%20own%20foreign%20concertgoers%2C%20and%20whose%20fans%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Singapore.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Philippines%20should%20not%20%26quot%3Bjust%20let%20things%20like%20these%20pass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Singapore%20PM%20confirmed%20that%20Ms%20Swift%20was%20provided%20with%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20incentives%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20government%20fund%20created%20to%20revive%20Singapore's%20tourism%20sector%20following%20the%20Covid-19%20outbreak.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20very%20successful%20arrangement.%20I%20don't%20see%20that%20as%20being%20unfriendly.%20Sometimes%20one%20country%20makes%20a%20deal%2C%20sometimes%20another%20country%20does.%20I%20don't%20explicitly%20say%20'you%20will%20come%20here%20only%20on%20condition%20that%20you'll%20not%20go%20to%20other%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20suggested%20that%20when%20Ms%20Swift%20per