arendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20family.%20In%20their%20perspective%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20had%20'insulted'%20Modi.%20Paradoxically%2C%20they%20also%20argued%20that%20Lalu's%20remarks%20would%20boomerang%20on%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20inflicting%20a%20heavy%20toll.%20Some%20even%20ventured%20to%20predict%20that%20Modi%20would%20secure%20a%20substantial%20victory%2C%20akin%20to%20his%20triumphs%20in%202014%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20had%20mocked%20Modi's%20background%20as%20a%20'Chaiwala'%20(tea%20seller)%2C%20and%20in%202019%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20used%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChaukidar%20Chor%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(the%20guard%20is%20the%20thief)%20jibe%20against%20Modi.%20On%20both%20the%20occasions%2C%20Modi%20utilised%20these%20attacks%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20opposition%20assaults.%20It%20was%20asserted%20that%20Modi's%20electoral%20triumph%20was%20facilitated%20by%20the%20opposition's%20'abuse'%2C%20which%20he%20adeptly%20leveraged%20to%20his%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi's%20Counter-attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Modi%20has%20attempted%20to%20mount%20a%20counterattack%20on%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20He%20seized%20upon%20Lalu's%20mention%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EParivar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(family)%20and%20coined%20a%20new%20slogan%2C%20'%3Cem%3EMai%20Bhi%20Modi%20ka%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(I%20am%20also%20Modi's%20family).%20Cabinet%20ministers%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20chief%20ministers%2C%20party%20officials%2C%20and%20cadre%2C%20were%20quick%20to%20add%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMai%20Bhi%20Modi%20ka%20parivar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20into%20their%20social%20media%20bios.%20This%20strategy%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20we%20saw%20in%202019%20when%20Rahul's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChaukidar%20Chor%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20phrase%20was%20transformed%20into%20'Mai%20Bhi%20chaukidar'%20(I%20too%20am%20a%20guard).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notion%20that%20elections%20in%20India%20could%20be%20swayed%20by%20a%20single%20statement%20is%20wishful%20thinking.%20Such%20a%20simplistic%20argument%20reflects%20lazy%20articulation%2C%20lacking%20an%20understanding%20of%20Indian%20realities.%20For%20parties%20and%20leaders%2C%20such%20remarks%2C%20at%20best%2C%20are%20used%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20launch%20counter-attacks.%20Elections%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20won%20or%20lost%20on%20genuine%20issues.%20While%20politicians%20may%20attempt%20to%20shift%20public%20focus%2C%20success%20in%20doing%20so%20is%20rare.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019%20were%20not%20won%20or%20lost%20because%20of%20the%20non-serious%20statements%20of%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Congress%20Really%20Lost%20The%202014%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202014%20elections%20signalled%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20India's%20electoral%20history.%20Corruption%20allegations%20had%20eroded%20the%20Congress's%20credibility%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20that%20a%20change%20of%20government%20was%20imminent.%20Modi%20astutely%20capitalised%20on%20public%20discontent%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20framing%20the%20election%20as%20a%20referendum%20on%20its%20politics%2C%20dynasty%2C%20and%20entitlement%2C%20intertwined%20with%20the%20broader%20narrative%20of%20Hindutva.%20He%20projected%20himself%20as%20a%20national%20saviour%20with%20solutions%20to%20all%20of%20India's%20problems.%20Modi's%20political%20acumen%2C%20combined%20with%20Congress's%20lackluster%20campaign%20and%20demoralised%20cadre%2C%20ensured%20his%20victory.%20Aiyar's%20%26quot%3BChaiwala%26quot%3B%20jibe%20added%20further%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%2C%20providing%20additional%20fodder%20for%20Modi's%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Modi%20faced%20challenges%20until%20the%20Pulwama%20incident%20reshaped%20the%20political%20landscape.%20Amidst%20concerns%20that%20Modi%20might%20not%20secure%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20heightened%20nationalism%20following%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Balakot%20airstrike%20overshadowed%20other%20issues.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChaukidar%20Chor%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20statement%20faded%20into%20obscurity%20as%20Modi's%20narrative%20of%20national%20security%20and%20strong%20leadership%20prevailed.%20The%20BJP%20secured%20a%20resounding%20victory%20with%20303%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrand%20Modi%20In%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20secured%20victory%20in%20assembly%20elections%20in%20three%20states%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20in%20December%202018.%20Prior%20to%20these%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20faced%20setbacks%2C%20failing%20to%20secure%20wins%20in%20Karnataka's%20assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20struggling%20in%20Gujarat%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%20However%2C%20following%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Pulwama%2C%20which%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%2039%20CRPF%20personnel%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20surgical%20strike%20in%20Balakot%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%2C%20heightened%20nationalism%20dominated%20the%20discourse.%20The%20rallying%20cry%20of%20'%3Cem%3EPakistan%20ko%20ghus%20ke%20mara%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(we%20went%20into%20Pakistan%20and%20took%20revenge)%20became%20the%20dominant%20theme%2C%20overshadowing%20other%20issues.%20By%20the%20time%20votes%20were%20cast%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20earlier%20remarks%20about%20Modi%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChaukidar%20Chor%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20statement%2C%20had%20faded%20into%20obscurity.%20Brand%20Modi%20emerged%20victorious%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20securing%20303%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20in%20the%20past%2C%20voters%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20likely%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20based%20on%20their%20perception%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20performance%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Modi%20has%20cultivated%20an%20image%20of%20change%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20emphasising%20reduced%20corruption%2C%20enhanced%20security%2C%20and%20increased%20global%20stature%20for%20India.%20His%20government's%20response%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20medical%20crisis%20during%20Covid-19%2C%20including%20free%20vaccination%20for%20140%20crore%20people%20and%20free%20ration%20for%2080%20crore%20poor%20citizens%2C%20has%20been%20highlighted.%20However%2C%20these%20claims%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20can%20be%20contested%20legitimately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Challenges%20This%20Time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20united%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20INDIA%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20undermining%20democracy%2C%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20to%20target%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20intimidating%20opposition%20leaders.%20Opinion%20polls%20consistently%20highlight%20concerns%20over%20rising%20prices%2C%20unemployment%2C%20and%20threats%20to%20minority%20rights.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20right-wing%20allies%20are%20accused%20of%20openly%20targeting%20some%20social%20groups%2C%20while%20government%20agencies%20are%20criticised%20for%20their%20perceived%20inaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20suggesting%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20decided%20solely%20by%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20statements%20challenges%20the%20collective%20wisdom%20of%20the%20voter.%20It%20implies%20that%2C%20even%20after%2077%20years%20of%20independence%2C%20voters%20have%20not%20embraced%20democratic%20consciousness%20and%20are%20still%20guided%20by%20herd%20mentality%2C%20allowing%20leaders%20to%20evade%20accountability%20for%20their%20actions.%20However%2C%20historical%20examples%20suggest%20otherwise%3B%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20defeat%20after%20the%20emergency%20in%201977%20and%20subsequent%20resurgence%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20trust%20placed%20in%20leaders%20like%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20illustrate%20the%20electorate's%20innate%20wisdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20For%20Flavour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20society%20is%20dynamic.%20While%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20granted%20two%20opportunities%20to%20govern%2C%20convincing%20voters%20of%20their%20worthiness%20for%20a%20third%20term%20won't%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20opposition%2C%20led%20by%20INDIA%2C%20must%20undertake%20substantial%20efforts%20before%20staking%20a%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrivolous%20statements%20may%20add%20flavour%20to%20political%20discourse%2C%20like%20a%20chutney%20does%20to%20a%20meal%2C%20but%20they%20can%20never%20be%20a%20substitute%20for%20substantive%20policy%20discussions%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20influence%20they%20have%20on%20people's%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709691780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fsg54kb1o_modi-lalu_625x300_04_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-2024-can-a-single-slogan-alter-poll-outcome-not-possible-5184776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lalu%20Yadav's%20statement%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20family%20can't%20change%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20elections.%20Elections%20are%20won%20and%20lost%20over%20genuine%20issues%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-2024-can-a-single-slogan-alter-poll-outcome-not