rmerly%20Twitter)%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20and%20people%20promoting%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Shambhu%2C%20Khanauri%20and%20Dabwali%20borders%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20farmer%20unions%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Jagjeet%20Singh%20Dallewal%20from%20the%20SKM%20Non-Political%20and%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20of%20the%20KMM%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20demanding%20legally%20guaranteed%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSP)%2C%20justice%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20case%20and%20the%20waiving%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20loans%20for%20over%2020%20days%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20for%20the%20third%20time%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20withheld%20social%20media%20accounts%20ever%20since%20the%20protest%20started%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20too%2C%20the%20government%20had%20withheld%20over%20a%20dozen%20social%20media%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20the%20official%20pages%20of%20farmer%20unions%20and%20their%20supporters%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%20on%20the%20night%20of%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20particularly%20those%20on%20X%2C%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20were%20again%20withheld%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%20on%20February%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20union%20leaders%20termed%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98modus%20operandi%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20where%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20being%20repeatedly%20withheld%20in%20bulk%20whenever%20they%20gave%20a%20call%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20farmer%20union%20leader%20Gurpreet%20Sangha%20said%20that%20overnight%2C%20around%20100%20social%20media%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20farmers%2C%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20and%20people%20supporting%20the%20protest%20were%20withheld%20in%20India%20on%20March%204%2C%20exactly%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%20for%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20date%2C%20the%20government%20has%20withheld%20my%20three%20X%20accounts%2C%20which%20I%20made%20after%20each%20one%20of%20them%20was%20blocked%20in%20India.%20We%20have%20decided%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20this%20case.%20Our%20legal%20team%20was%20working%20on%20it%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangha%20said%20that%20the%20government%20does%20not%20want%20their%20voice%20to%20reach%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%E2%80%99s%20message%20is%20clear%3A%20that%20they%20will%20not%20even%20let%20the%20farmers%20speak%2C%20leave%20alone%20the%20debate%20of%20right%20or%20wrong.%20Basically%2C%20the%20government%20fears%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20that%20is%20why%20they%20were%20banning%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20killing%20its%20own%20people%20should%20be%20the%20last%20resort%20of%20any%20regime%2C%20but%20either%20in%20panic%20or%20in%20despair%2C%20the%20government%20has%20misacted%20big%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20March%206%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%2C%20Sangha%20said%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20100%20farmers%20or%2010%2C000%2C%20they%20will%20simply%20reach%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20Delhi%20and%20sit%20there%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20purely%20organic%20announcement%2C%20where%20farmers%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20other%20than%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20would%20lead%20the%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20farmers%20said%20that%20this%20time%2C%20the%20government%20was%20also%20targeting%20those%20accounts%20which%20were%20promoting%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cause%20since%20the%202021-21%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20was%20Sheena%20Sawhney%2C%20a%20dentist%20and%20US%20citizen%2C%20who%20said%20she%20has%20been%20involved%20with%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%20since%20the%202020-21%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20led%20a%20huge%20group%20of%20people%20in%20the%20US%20and%20campaigned%20against%20the%20farm%20laws.%20I%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20all%20the%20SKM%20leaders%20like%20Rakesh%20Tikait%2C%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20and%20others%20to%20mobilise%20people%20but%20nobody%20blocked%20my%20Twitter%20account%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20has%20just%20started%2C%20the%20government%20withheld%20my%20X%20account%2C%20which%20basically%20hints%20at%20moles%20within%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20groups%20who%20were%20sharing%20our%20information%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawhney%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%20started%20withholding%20social%20media%20accounts%20this%20time%2C%20she%20thought%20she%20would%20be%20safe%20owing%20to%20her%20US%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20rattled%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20action.%20Even%20if%20the%20government%20did%20not%20retrieve%20my%20X%20account%2C%20I%20would%20make%20a%20new%20account%20and%20continue%20to%20raise%20%5Bmy%5D%20voice%20for%20farmers.%20I%20was%20trolled%20and%20labelled%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99%20for%20supporting%20farmers%20but%20the%20government%20never%20took%20any%20action%20against%20the%20trolls%20and%20it%20hurts.%20I%20spoke%20for%20farmers%20earlier%3B%20I%20will%20speak%20even%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-based%20dentist%20said%20that%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20just%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20government%20does%20not%20want%20any%20protest%20at%20this%20stage.%20But%20supporters%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cause%20will%20write%20letters%20to%20senators%2C%20council%20members%20and%20higher%20authorities%20in%20the%20US%20to%20gain%20momentum%20for%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20people%20who%20supported%20George%20Floyd%E2%80%99s%20protest%20in%20the%20US%20were%20questioning%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20the%20tragic%20killing%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurshamshir%20Singh%2C%20a%20lawyer-turned-independent%20journalist%20from%20Patiala%20whose%20X%20account%20was%20withheld%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20does%20not%20want%20any%20information%20about%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20to%20reach%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%20of%20March%206%20is%20the%20biggest%20reason%20why%20so%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20blocked%20in%20India.%20It%20has%20almost%20become%20a%20modus%20operandi%20of%20the%20government%20to%20block%20social%20media%20accounts%20whenever%20they%20see%20a%20potential%20of%20mass%20mobilisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20knows%20that%20nobody%20is%20going%20to%20hold%20them%20accountable%20for%20this%20action%2C%20hence%20such%20emboldened%20actions.%20It%20is%20also%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20a%20fear%20psychosis%20among%20people%20related%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20sad%20that%20the%20country%20was%20heading%20towards%20an%20authoritarian%20regime%20and%20in%20case%20you%20are%20from%20Punjab%2C%20you%20are%20more%20prone%20than%20others.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20others%2C%20Samita%20Kaur%2C%20an%20independent%20researcher%20from%20Chandigarh%20working%20for%20farmers%20and%20who%20was%20also%20running%20a%20campaign%20titled%20%E2%80%98We%20support%20our%20farmers%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20that%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20Sawhney%20and%20to%20the%20KMM%20were%20also%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20simply%20sharing%20news%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20government%20was%20also%20targeting%20those%20accounts%20who%20were%20using%20the%20hashtags%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20We%20had%20just%20shared%20an%20article%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20on%20the%20KMM%20page%2C%20after%20which%20our%20account%20was%20withheld%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamita%20Kaur%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20%E2%80%98No%20farmer%2C%20No%20food%E2%80%99%20campaign%20along%20with%20her%20peers%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20farming%20was%20going%20to%20the%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20corporations%20want%20to%20control%20and%20change%20the%20eating%20habits%20of%20the%20people.%20They%20want%20to%20decide%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20eat%2C%20hence%20the%20fight%20between%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20corporates%2Fgovernment%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20government%20had%20withheld%20the%20X%20account%20of%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20and%20that%20of%20his%20web%20portal%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGoan%20Savera%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Punia%20was%20was%20exclusively%20covering%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20the%20Shambu%20and%20Khanuari%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20his%20Delhi-based%20colleague%20Garvit%20Garg%20started%20posting%20news%20and%20updates%20about%20the%20protest%20through%20his%20personal%20X%20account.%20On%20the%20night%20of%20March%204%2C%20Garg%E2%80%99s%20account%20was%20also%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Garg%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20blocked%20all%20channels%20of%20information%20dissemination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20just%20an%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%20but%20a%20professional%20loss%20for%20us.%20Independent%20journalists%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20gather%20factual%20news%20and%20sustain%20their%20work.%20We%20are%20being%20continuously%20targeted%20by%20the%20government.%20Earlier%20the%20government%20had%20withheld%20the%20official%20page%20of%20%3Cem%3EGoan%20Savera%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20that%20of%20its%20editor%2C%20Mandeep%20Punia.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20targeted%20me%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarvit%20said%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20was%20to%20muzzle%20every%20voice%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20total%20blackout%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20news%20everywhere.%20See%2C%20we%20could%20not%20even%20share%20the%20information%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%20of%20March%206%20on%20social%20media.%20It%20is%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%2C%20even%20those%20working%20with%20bigger%20media%20houses%20will%20also%20be%20attacked.%20Right%20now%2C%20we%20do%20not%20even%20see%20any%20way%20of%20fighting%20back%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20legal%20team%20of%20the%20KMM%2C%20led%20by%20its%20coordinator%2C%20advocate%20Akhil%20Chaudhary%20from%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%2C%20and%20Anjali%20Sheoran%20from%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20some%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20blocked%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20this%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20our%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20plan%20to%20challenge%20it%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%20have%20urged%20all%20affected%20individuals%20to%20join%20our%20petition%20and%20contact%20our%20team%20for%20necessary%20paperwork%2C%20including%20signing%20the%20%3Cem%3Evakalatnama%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20completing%20other%20formalities%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709661192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16091726%2FIMG_20240215_150214_364-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmuzzling-voices-government-withholds-100-social-media-accounts-ahead-of-next-delhi-chalo-call%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20for%20the%20third%20time%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20withheld%20social%20media%20accounts%20ever%20since%20the%20protest%20started%20on%20February%2013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmuzzling-voices-government-withholds-100-social-media-accounts-ahead-of-next-delhi-chalo-call%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kotak%20Life%20Insurance%20launches%20non-linked%20par%20product%20Kotak%20G.A.I.N%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709660611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-09%2F02%2Ffull%2F1662127346-987.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkotak-life-insurance-launches-non-linked-par-product-kotak-g-a-i-n-124030501116_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20sector%20life%20insurer%20Kotak%20Life%20Insurance%20on%20Tuesday%20launched%20a%20non-linked%20participating%20product%20Kotak%20G.A.I.N%20which%20offers%20long-term%20saving%20or%20income%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkotak-life-insurance-launches-non-linked-par-product-kotak-g-a-i-n-124030501116_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fkotak-life-insurance-launches-non-linked-par-product-kotak-g-a-i-n-124030501116_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%