herefore%2C%20none%20of%20the%20points%20put%20forward%20by%20SEBI%20are%20binding%2C%20i.e.%20create%20a%20new%20law%20or%20policy.%20They%20are%20simply%20recommendations%20laid%20down%20for%20further%20conversation%20and%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20consultation%20paper%2C%20they%20broadly%20lay%20down%20three%20issues%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20the%20nomination%20process%20apply%20to%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20role%20of%20nominees%20with%20respect%20to%20legal%20heirs%20and%20wills%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20method%20of%20appointing%20nominees%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20very%20clearly%20underscored%20that%20nomination%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98entirely%20optional%20process%E2%80%99.%20The%20recommendation%20SEBI%20makes%20is%20that%20in%20a%20single%20person-held%20demat%20account%2C%20a%20clear%20declaration%20be%20made%20that%20they%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20assign%20a%20nominee.%20This%20is%20simply%20a%20measure%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20procedural%20ease%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20before%20reading%20the%20paper%20is%20the%20distinction%20between%20nominees%20and%20legal%20heirs%2C%20which%20can%20often%20be%20a%20point%20of%20confusion%20for%20a%20layperson.%20As%20highlighted%20by%20various%20financial%20experts%20and%20publications%2C%20nominees%20are%20not%20legal%20heirs%20to%20the%20securities.%20They%20are%20simply%20temporary%20custodians%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20the%20securities%20are%20correctly%20transferred%20to%20the%20legal%20heirs%2C%20as%20per%20a%20will%20or%20law.%20They%20are%20akin%20to%20an%20executor%20of%20a%20will%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20but%20for%20a%20specific%20asset%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20SEBI%20provides%20suggestions%20on%20processes%20for%20how%20nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20and%20how%20they%20must%20act.%20Nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20through%20digital%20methods%20for%20ease%2C%20however%2C%20safety%20is%20kept%20in%20mind%20in%20this%20process%20as%20well%20by%20ensuring%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20digital%20signature%20or%20Aadhaar-based%20eSigns.%20One%20needs%20to%20provide%20identification%20of%20the%20proposed%20nominee(s)%20as%20well.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20physical%20nomination%20through%20thumb%20impressions%20and%20verification%20also%20continues%20to%20be%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20various%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20sole%20accounts%2C%20joint%20accounts%2C%20simultaneous%20deaths%20of%20account%20holders%20among%20others%2C%20and%20how%20a%20nominee%20will%20be%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20account%20for%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20each%20case.%20It%20also%20lays%20down%20which%20legal%20heirs%20are%20entitled%20to%20the%20securities%20in%20cases%20of%20joint%20accounts%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20read%20a%20more%20detailed%20summary%20of%20the%20paper%2C%20and%20provide%20your%20feedback%20on%20it%20by%208%20March%2C%202024%2C%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F48w8AwO%5C%22%3ECivis%20Platform%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivis%20is%20a%20civic-tech%20organisation%20that%20aggregates%20and%20simplifies%20draft%20laws%20and%20policies%20that%20are%20open%20for%20public%20feedback%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20the%20process%20as%20simple%20for%20you%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20paper%20has%20been%20hosted%20with%20a%20summary%20that%20you%20can%20read%20in%20an%20accessible%20format%2C%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Hindi%2C%20and%20give%20your%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20written%20by%20the%20team%20at%20Civis.vote%2C%20a%20non-profit%20platform%20that%20works%20to%20build%20dialogue%20between%20governments%20and%20citizens%2C%20using%20technology%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20two.