ank%5C%22%3EHyderabad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20dish%20is%20made%20by%20slow-cooking%20a%20mixture%20of%20lentils%2C%20usually%20a%20combination%20of%20wheat%2C%20barley%2C%20and%20sometimes%20rice%2C%20along%20with%20meat%20(typically%20lamb%20or%20chicken)%2C%20until%20it%20reaches%20a%20thick%2C%20porridge-like%20consistency.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20slow%20cooking%20process%2C%20often%20lasting%20several%20hours%2C%20allows%20the%20flavours%20to%20meld%20together%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20rich%20and%20velvety%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20hundreds%20of%20people%20visiting%20the%20place%20everyday%2C%20you%20should%20try%20Pista%20House%E2%80%99s%20haleem%20at%20least%20once%20in%20your%20life.%20Garnished%20with%20fried%20onions%2C%20fresh%20cilantro%2C%20mint%20leaves%2C%20and%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%2C%20Pista%20House%20Haleem%20is%20a%20feast%20for%20the%20senses%2C%20captivating%20diners%20with%20its%20irresistible%20aroma%20and%20sumptuous%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Haleem%20-%20a%20must-try%20dish%20of%20Hyderabad.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20